{"article_id":"7l4hr7KOE5Uuu79b","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Obama continues to alter his signature promise","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"in selling the Affordable Care Act back in 2009 and 2010 .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"`` If you like your plan ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"you can keep your plan , ''","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"he said back then .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"But that simple pledge has had to change","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"as the Affordable Care Act has been implemented","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"and a small percentage of Americans , albeit millions of people , have received cancellation notices from their insurance companies .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"And for the second time in two weeks , he 's tweaked the line .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"When President Obama spoke Monday night to a group of supporters ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"he said :","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"`` While virtually every insurer is offering new , better plans","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"and competing for these folks ' business ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"I realize","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that can be scary for people","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"if you just get some notice like that . ''","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"`` If you had or have one of these plans","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"before the Affordable Care Act came into law","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"and you really like that plan ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"what we said was , you could keep it","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"if has n't changed","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"since the law 's passed , ''","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"added Obama .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"`` You 're grandfathered in , ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"although he again noted","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"insurance companies had the power","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"to change it themselves .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"CNN White House Senior Correspondent Jim Acosta asked White House Spokesman Jay Carney on Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"if the president could go back ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"would he `` use the same words again ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"and promise Americans","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"they could keep their plans ?","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"`` Well , the president ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"as awesomely powerful","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"as the office is ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"ca n't go back in time , ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Carney said .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` And what the president is focused on is what we are all focused on","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"which is getting this right for the American people . ''","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"`` It is on us , ''","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Carney later added .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"`` Let me be clear ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"I 'm not -","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"I am embracing the responsibility","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"that the administration and","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"that everyone involved in the market place","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"has ,","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"to make sure","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"that those individuals are getting the information","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"that they need . ''","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"The President made his comments Monday in an address to Organizing for Action , the pro-Obama group","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"formed from the President 's 2012 re-election campaign .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Even though some people are getting kicked off existing plans ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Obama has argued","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"they 're probably going to get a better deal .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"`` Now , insurers are offering these new options ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and they do n't just want to keep their current policyholders ;","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"they want to cover the uninsured , too , ''","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"he told supporters .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"`` And","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"because of the competition between insurers , and the new health care tax credits ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"most people will be able to buy better plans for the same price or even cheaper than what they 've gotten before .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Now , some Americans with higher incomes will pay more on the front end for better insurance with better benefits and better protections","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"that could eventually help them a lot ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"even if right now they 'd rather be paying less . ''","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"He made similar points at a health care event in Boston last Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"The new line is a far cry from the shorter , bumper sticker ready pledge","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"he made","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"as he sought to calm nerves","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"that health insurance reform would not ruin plans","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that Americans liked and were comfortable with","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"even though many of those plans did n't cover things like prescription drugs , hospital stays or maternity care .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"It was n't a one off back in 2009 and 2010 and even later during his 2012 re-election campaign .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"New York Magazine put together a montage of the very many iterations of it .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"But it turns out the president did n't have the power","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"to make that pledge .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"As insurance companies upgrade plans","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"to comply with new Obamacare coverage rules ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"they are dropping plans for potentially millions of Americans","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"who buy their insurance on the individual health insurance market .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Insurance companies appear to be doing this for a variety of reasons ;","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"some are pulling all their plans from certain states","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"where they have fewer subscribers","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"in order to save money ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"others seem to be .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Back in 2009 , as a White House correspondent for ABC , CNN 's Jake Tapper challenged the president on his promise .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"And even back then , there appeared to be an asterisk .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"`` Well , no , no ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"I mean -","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"when I say","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"if you have your plan","depth":17},{"id":92,"text":"and you like it","depth":19},{"id":93,"text":"and your doctor has a plan ,","depth":19},{"id":94,"text":"or you have a doctor","depth":19},{"id":95,"text":"and you like your doctor","depth":19},{"id":96,"text":"that you do n't have to change plans ,","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"what I 'm saying is the government is not going to make you change plans under health reform , ''","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"Obama replied .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"Ah ... the government is not going to make you change plans .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Though the government might impose a situation","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"that would cause a change of plans .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"So the promise was never quite as presented .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"And yet the president kept presenting it that way .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"But that caveat did n't make it into the subsequent campaign speeches","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"that featured the line .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"The cancellations will not affect most Americans ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"but they could hurt public support for the law .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Just 17 % of Americans said","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"they 'll be better off under the law ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"but 41 % said","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"it wo n't have much of an effect on them ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"according to a CNN/ORC International poll","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"conducted in late September ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"just before the HealthCare.gov website went live .","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"At that time four in ten said","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"they would be worse off under the law .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"Those numbers are similar to a Gallup poll","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"conducted just over a week ago ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"in which 36 % of Americans said","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"they did n't think","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"that in the long run the Affordable Care Act would make much of a difference to their family 's health care situation .","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Just over a third said","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"the health care law would make matters worse ,","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"and one in four said","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"that Obamacare would make things better .","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"Rollout of the exchange websites","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"that are supposed to allow Americans without insurance to shop from a selection of plans side-by-side","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"has been troubled ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"to say the least .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"The website has been plagued by glitches , crashes ,","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"and is currently the subject of a Congressional investigation .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"Frustration with the law and the changes","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"it causes in the health insurance landscape","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"could be temporary growing pains","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"as Americans get used to the reforms .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"But the frustration is likely to outlast problems with the website","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"as Americans focus more on the cost of plans","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"offered under Obamacare","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"and on the choices available .","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"CNN reported Monday on notes from an Obama administration `` war room '' meeting","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"where officials expressed concern","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"once Americans had access to more information about the plans available ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"they might experience sticker shock .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"An architect of the Affordable Care Act , MIT professor Jonathan Gruber , told CNN 's Wolf Blitzer recently","depth":4},{"id":146,"text":"that most Americans will benefit from the law","depth":5},{"id":147,"text":"as it stabilizes the insurance market ,","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"fosters competition","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"and guarantees coverage for almost all Americans .","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"Most Americans get insurance from either the government or their employer","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"and wo n't be affected much by the law ,","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"`` About 5 to 6 percent get it on their","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"and some of them will pay more ,","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"the young and health and not poor will pay more","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"to get their health insurance .","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"It 's a lot of people ,","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"but its small relative to the people","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"who are going to gain","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"and very small relative to the people","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"who are n't affected , ''","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"added Gruber .","depth":6},{"id":163,"text":"But he also ceded","depth":6},{"id":164,"text":"that there will be winners and losers","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"as the law is implemented .","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"Some people will pay more","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"and be forced to change their insurance .","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"That 's a small percentage of the country , but a large number of people .","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"`` Very very few people have to pay more","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"and not get better insurance .","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"That 's a very small fraction , ''","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"said Gruber .","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"`` Most of the people","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"who will have to pay more","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"will get better insurance","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"than what they had before . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":353,"left":0,"right":352,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":352,"left":320,"right":351,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":320,"left":252,"right":319,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":203,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":185,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":178,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":183,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":183,"left":180,"right":182,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":180,"left":179,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":182,"left":6,"right":181,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":186,"right":201,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":201,"left":190,"right":200,"relation":"joint","nucleari